    "The other task was to propose a CTR calculation algorithm based on deep learning for the quantitative assessment of cardiomegaly.",
    "Similarly, internal, multicentre and prospective validations were performed to evaluate the performance of the proposed algorithm (Fig. 1b).",
    "Finally, the above two tasks were integrated into a framework that could assist radiologists in reviewing CXRs in clinical practice.",
    "We consecutively collected 315,072 original CXRs from 159,996 patients at the Department of Radiology, Second Affiliated Hospital, Army Medical University (AMU), between August 2011 and December 2021.",
    "Lateral or anteroposterior CXRs, CXRs from patients under the age of eighteen, and duplicate CXRs were excluded from the study."
